The paper deals with the analysis of large-scale Internet traffic, which is a topic that falls under the category of computer networks (cs.NI). The use of neural networks and machine learning techniques to analyze this traffic also suggests that the paper could be classified under the categories of cybersecurity (cs.CR), social and information networks (cs.SI), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), and machine learning (cs.LG).
